  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img alt=\"Translation\" src=\"../images/T.gif\"/>\n<strong>Latin (with quotations in Greek)</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>\"For once I myself saw with my own eyes the Sibyl\n        at Cumae hanging in a cage, and when the boys said to\n        her: 'Sibyl, what do you want?' she replied, 'I want to\n        die.'\" </p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Sibyl.htm\"><font>The Cumaean Sibyl</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"publication_data.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>The Meaning of the Notes</td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
